Title: UAE Minister to attend cyber meet
Content: Lt. Gen. Sheik Saif bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Deputy Prime Minister and Minister for Interior, UAE, will be the guest of honour at a two-day international cyber security and policing conference scheduled
